## ðŸ“š The 3 PgMP Domains

### Domain 1: Program Strategy Alignment (16%)
- Aligning program to organizational strategy
- Benefits identification
- Program business case
- â†’ Folder: `/domains/01-strategy/`

### Domain 2: Benefits Management (16%)
- Benefits planning, delivery, transition
- Measuring outcomes vs outputs
- Sustaining benefits beyond project
- â†’ Folder: `/domains/02-benefits/`

### Domain 3: Stakeholder Engagement (16%)
- Stakeholder identification & analysis
- Communication planning
- Managing stakeholder expectations
- â†’ Folder: `/domains/03-stakeholders/`

### Domain 4: Governance (16%)
- Program governance frameworks
- Reporting structures
- Decision-making authority
- â†’ Folder: `/domains/04-governance/`

### Domain 5: Program Life Cycle Management (36%)
- Program formulation, planning, execution, closure
- Component management
- Risk and issue management
- â†’ Folder: `/domains/05-lifecycle/`

